  <div id="prev-travel" class="preventive-content active">
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">🚕</div>
      <h4>Verify Your Cab Before Boarding</h4>
      <ul><li>Screenshot ride details and WhatsApp to trusted contact</li><li>Sit behind the driver — never in the front</li><li>Share trip via app's live tracking feature</li><li>Cancel and rebook if anything feels off</li></ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">🏔️</div>
      <h4>Mountain Road & Trek Safety in HP</h4>
      <ul><li>Always register at nearest Forest/Tourism office before trekking</li><li>Carry HP tourist police helpline: 01772-812344</li><li>Inform your hotel/homestay of your planned route</li><li>Avoid isolated mountain paths alone after 5PM</li></ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">📍</div>
      <h4>Share Live Location Always</h4>
      <ul><li>Google Maps "Share Live Location" with parent for every solo trip</li><li>Tell someone your exact route and arrival time</li><li>Have a family code word: "call the doctor" = call police</li><li>Check in every 30 minutes on remote HP mountain routes</li></ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">🚌</div>
      <h4>HRTC Bus Safety in HP</h4>
      <ul><li>HP roadways buses (HRTC) have women-reserved front seats — use them</li><li>Stand near the conductor on empty routes</li><li>Avoid isolated bus stops after 7PM in hill areas</li><li>Use Shimla City Bus or app-based taxis in Shimla & Dharamshala</li></ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">🔋</div>
      <h4>Keep Your Phone Emergency-Ready</h4>
      <ul><li>Carry a power bank (min 10,000 mAh) in HP's remote areas</li><li>Save emergency contacts as "ICE Mom", "ICE Dad"</li><li>Enable power-button SOS: volume down + power 5× on Android</li><li>Note: signal can be weak in interior HP — download offline maps</li></ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prev-card">
      <div class="prev-card-icon">🚌</div>
      <h4>Auto & Local Transport in HP</h4>
      <ul><li>Note the vehicle registration before boarding</li><li>Prefer app-based taxis (Ola/Rapido) in Shimla, Dharamshala, Manali</li><li>Avoid isolated routes during snowfall or after dark</li><li>Carry HP Tourist Police number: 01772-812344</li></ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="prev-digital" class="preventive-content">
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🔒</div><h4>Social Media Privacy</h4><ul><li>Set Instagram, Facebook to Private</li><li>Never post daily routine, college timings, or home address</li><li>Turn off location tags on all photos</li><li>Disable "People Nearby" on WhatsApp</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">📵</div><h4>Protect Against Cyber Stalking</h4><ul><li>Screenshot all harassing messages first — then block</li><li>Report to cybercrime.gov.in or call 1930</li><li>Do not engage or respond to harassers</li><li>Use different usernames across platforms</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🖼️</div><h4>Prevent Photo & Video Misuse</h4><ul><li>Never share intimate photos — no exceptions</li><li>Check which apps have camera/gallery access — revoke unnecessary ones</li><li>Enable two-step verification on all accounts</li><li>Report morphed images to 1930 immediately</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">💳</div><h4>Online Financial Safety</h4><ul><li>Never share OTP with anyone</li><li>Verify job offers and matrimonial profiles carefully</li><li>No legitimate organization asks for money upfront</li><li>Report financial fraud at 1930 immediately</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">📱</div><h4>Install Safety Apps</h4><ul><li>Himmat Plus (Delhi Police) — shake to send SOS</li><li>bSafe — fake call feature and follower mode</li><li>Shake2Safety — works when screen is locked</li><li>HP Police app — direct complaint filing from Himachal Pradesh</li></ul></div>
  </div>

  <div id="prev-night" class="preventive-content">
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🌙</div><h4>Walking Alone at Night in HP</h4><ul><li>Stay on well-lit, busy roads even if it means a longer route</li><li>Avoid HP hill paths, forests, and isolated lanes after dark</li><li>Walk confidently — don't look lost or distracted</li><li>Keep 112 ready to dial in one tap</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🔦</div><h4>Equip Yourself</h4><ul><li>Personal alarm (loud siren) — ₹150–300 on Amazon</li><li>Pepper spray is legal in India — keep in an accessible pocket</li><li>Torch/flashlight essential in HP's frequent power outages</li><li>Charge phone to 100% before going out</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🛑</div><h4>If You Feel Followed</h4><ul><li>Enter the nearest open shop, dhaba, or petrol pump immediately</li><li>Do NOT go home directly — never reveal your address</li><li>Shout "FIRE!" loudly — more people respond than to "Help"</li><li>Call 100 or 112 and describe your exact location</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">📞</div><h4>Fake Call Technique</h4><ul><li>Pretend to be on a call if you feel followed</li><li>Say loudly: "I am near [landmark], reaching in 5 minutes, bhaiya wait karo"</li><li>Apps like bSafe simulate incoming calls on demand</li><li>Buys time to move toward a safer location</li></ul></div>
  </div>

  <div id="prev-home" class="preventive-content">
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🔐</div><h4>Home Security Basics</h4><ul><li>Never open the door without verifying — use peephole or intercom</li><li>Keep a door chain on while sleeping</li><li>Know all entry points to your residence</li><li>Keep a fully charged phone on your bedside</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🤝</div><h4>Build a Neighbourhood Network</h4><ul><li>Introduce yourself to 2–3 trusted neighbours</li><li>Share emergency contact numbers with them</li><li>Join your housing society's WhatsApp group</li><li>Alert neighbours about strangers loitering near your building</li></ul></div>
    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">🚪</div><h4>Verify People Entering Your Home</h4><ul><li>Verify Aadhaar of domestic helpers before hiring</li><li>Register domestic workers at local HP police station (free)</li><li>Use verified platforms like UrbanClap for electricians etc.</li><li>Never let unverified persons in when alone</li></ul></div>
  </div>

