    <div class="prev-card"><div class="prev-card-icon">📝</div><h4>Document Everything</h4><ul><li>Save harassing messages as screenshots immediately</li><li>Note dates, times, witnesses, and exact words used</li><li>Keep a private diary of incidents with dates</li><li>Store all evidence on cloud storage</li></ul></div>
