  <div class="tips-grid">
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">01</div><div><div class="tip-icon">📱</div><div class="tip-title">Share Live Location Always</div><div class="tip-desc">Whenever travelling alone — day or night — share your live location via Google Maps. Make it a non-negotiable daily habit especially on HP mountain routes.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">02</div><div><div class="tip-icon">🔋</div><div class="tip-title">Phone Charged = You're Armed</div><div class="tip-desc">Carry a power bank always — HP's remote areas have limited charging spots. Save ICE contacts at the top of your phonebook. Enable one-press SOS.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">03</div><div><div class="tip-icon">🚕</div><div class="tip-title">Verify Every Ride</div><div class="tip-desc">Match cab number, driver name and photo before entering. Screenshot and send to family. Sit behind the driver. State your destination aloud before moving.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">04</div><div><div class="tip-icon">👀</div><div class="tip-title">Stay Aware — One Earphone Off</div><div class="tip-desc">Never use both earphones in unfamiliar areas. Keep one ear free when walking on quiet HP mountain roads, forest paths, or at night.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">05</div><div><div class="tip-icon">🛡️</div><div class="tip-title">Install Safety Apps</div><div class="tip-desc">Himmat Plus, bSafe, or Shake2Safety. The HP Police app allows direct complaint filing from anywhere in Himachal Pradesh — download and test it.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">06</div><div><div class="tip-icon">🗣️</div><div class="tip-title">Trust Your Instincts Completely</div><div class="tip-desc">If something feels wrong — it is wrong. Leave immediately. You do not owe anyone an explanation. Your safety always comes first.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">07</div><div><div class="tip-icon">🔑</div><div class="tip-title">Carry Keys & Pepper Spray</div><div class="tip-desc">Keep keys in hand approaching your vehicle or home. Pepper spray is legal in India, fits in any pocket, and is highly effective. Especially useful on isolated HP trails.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-card"><div class="tip-num">08</div><div><div class="tip-icon">📸</div><div class="tip-title">Screenshot First — Then Block</div><div class="tip-desc">If harassed online — screenshot everything first as evidence, then block and report. Don't delete anything before reporting to 1930.</div></div></div>
